    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Corridors running along the tops of counterscarps and protected by embankments whose outer slopes form glacis. Continuous path around a fortress, covered by an additional rampart such as a counterscarp or a glacis.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
